---
title: Creamy Garlic Prawn Fettuccine with Leek, Lemony Parsley & Parmesan
description: Golden strands of fresh fettuccine combine with aromatic seasonings and meaty prawns to create a quick meal that feels a bit fancy. Add a squeeze of lemon juice and sprigs of rocket leaves for a pop of fresh and peppery flavour, then the chilli flakes for some heat, and dinner is complete.
